## üß¨ TCM Theory & Commentary

Y√¨sh√® BL-49 is level with P√≠sh≈´ BL-20, the back-shu point of the Spleen. Despite its name (Abode of Thought), psychological and emotional indications are notable by their absence in major classical texts.

